import { Flex, Spacer, Box, Center } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import Logo from "../atoms/Logo"
import MenuBar from "../atoms/MenuBar"

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Box as='header' h='70px' bg='rgb(239, 239, 239)' borderBottom='solid 4px rgba(26,187,154,.3)'>
            <Flex align='center' justify='space-between' h='70px'>
                <Box ml='20px'>
                    <Logo />    
                </Box>
                <Box>
                    <MenuBar />
                </Box>
            </Flex>
            <Box position='absolute' bottom='-4px' h='4px' bg='#1abb9a'></Box>
        </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default Header
